      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Q We write a great software, we know that so many people are going to use this, so many companies are going to use \nthis, many solo personals are going to use this, we develop something that great what would be next step?\n\nwe will market it, sell it,will start charging for it, this mindset is called the mindset of FOSS\nfree and open sourse softwares.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Q We write a great software, we know that so many people are going to use this, so many companies are going to use \nthis, many solo personals are going to use this, we develop something that great what would be next step?\n\nwe will market it, sell it,will start charging for it, this mindset is called the mindset of FOSS\nfree and open sourse softwares.",
