      "text": "Companies started using this since it was \nopen source and do some little chnages \nand given their own name, they have added binaries, utility s/w\nand Application s/w",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Companies started using this since it was \nopen source and do some little chnages \nand given their own name, they have added binaries, utility s/w\nand Application s/w",
      "autoResize": true,
