      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Processor\nHDD(Hardisk) -> Secondary memory\nPrimary Memory -> it is basically RAM and ROM\n",
