      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771264943613,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1 cache\n2 rem part of cache\n3 virtual memory\n4 rem part of HDD\n\nthis is how we manage speed and flow\nof data, when the data comes to processor it\nhas to come with the electricity speed, without\nany delays, lags",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1 cache\n2 rem part of cache\n3 virtual memory\n4 rem part of HDD\n\nthis is how we manage speed and flow\nof data, when the data comes to processor it\nhas to come with the electricity speed, without\nany delays, lags",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
