      "versionNonce": 1080995241,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772034352877,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CPP -> comes with core system level power, which is super fast, So the kind of system level\n    programming that can be done in CPP can be done no where else.\n\nJava -> The way it handles objects, no one else can do or the way it handle garbage or multi-\n    threading etc no one else can do. This is why it is great over there, bcz it makes it so \n    easy, so smooth at the same time so many functionalities can be targeted. \n\nPython -> we can code web pages, we can code applications, we can code SDKs, we can write \n    scripts like automation scripts and everything, everything almost can be done in Python.\n    It is that flexible. So it is flexible(doing everything) but not fast",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CPP -> comes with core system level power, which is super fast, So the kind of system level\n    programming that can be done in CPP can be done no where else.\n\nJava -> The way it handles objects, no one else can do or the way it handle garbage or multi-\n    threading etc no one else can do. This is why it is great over there, bcz it makes it so \n    easy, so smooth at the same time so many functionalities can be targeted. \n\nPython -> we can code web pages, we can code applications, we can code SDKs, we can write \n    scripts like automation scripts and everything, everything almost can be done in Python.\n    It is that flexible. So it is flexible(doing everything) but not fast",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "md7d1D0wY0MAKiQJtgf4l",
