    },
    {
      "id": "FLRVFiT0dTLvpesVwJK6r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1037.995186421342,
      "y": 26664.202167677915,
      "width": 1089,
      "height": 625,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bOn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 182396327,
      "version": 2051,
      "versionNonce": 13983015,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772041931461,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3 to 4 years from now, we don't even know how much we will see web development, which means\npicking up javascript and saying that we will make a long term career in it now is very risky.\nWe are not saying javascript will be eliminating, It will be there, But most of its work will\nbe done by AI. Going forward if there are careers that are to be booming, How will AI will \nimpact everything stuff like that ? How will job profiles be impacted? There are only few job\nprofiles that will going to sustain good in market. One very good profile is Devops.\nEven we will see lot of SDEs working as in terms of DevOps, When we will say Devops we are\ntalking about everything, It can be MLOps, It can be LLMOps, all kind of Ops Work that will\nsurvive. Due to that these things are not easily handled by Developer SO AI will take time on these\nthings to command over.\n\nAnother thing is Security, Network Security, Cloud Security and everything like that, Server\nhardening, System hardening this will sustain because we can't blindly trust AI to secure our\nthings. No matter howmuch AI will secure, We will always need someone to have a overwatch even\non AI.\n\nAnother thing is those Backend Developers who can develop core AI features. Who can manipulate AI\nwho can write AI, who can do the LLM works and all of this so this is AI engineering. This is \ngoing to survive alot. Here we will create ML algo, we will build agents, we will build custom\nLLMs. Creating custom LLMs itself comes up with various small domains, we are either working on \nRAGs or we are working on Fine tuning or AI ethics stuff like this.\n\nFrontend is not secure choice. AI can write good frontend for us to use good prompt.\n\nWe need to good at Ansible, Terraform, Kubernetis things like that.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3 to 4 years from now, we don't even know how much we will see web development, which means\npicking up javascript and saying that we will make a long term career in it now is very risky.\nWe are not saying javascript will be eliminating, It will be there, But most of its work will\nbe done by AI. Going forward if there are careers that are to be booming, How will AI will \nimpact everything stuff like that ? How will job profiles be impacted? There are only few job\nprofiles that will going to sustain good in market. One very good profile is Devops.\nEven we will see lot of SDEs working as in terms of DevOps, When we will say Devops we are\ntalking about everything, It can be MLOps, It can be LLMOps, all kind of Ops Work that will\nsurvive. Due to that these things are not easily handled by Developer SO AI will take time on these\nthings to command over.\n\nAnother thing is Security, Network Security, Cloud Security and everything like that, Server\nhardening, System hardening this will sustain because we can't blindly trust AI to secure our\nthings. No matter howmuch AI will secure, We will always need someone to have a overwatch even\non AI.\n\nAnother thing is those Backend Developers who can develop core AI features. Who can manipulate AI\nwho can write AI, who can do the LLM works and all of this so this is AI engineering. This is \ngoing to survive alot. Here we will create ML algo, we will build agents, we will build custom\nLLMs. Creating custom LLMs itself comes up with various small domains, we are either working on \nRAGs or we are working on Fine tuning or AI ethics stuff like this.\n\nFrontend is not secure choice. AI can write good frontend for us to use good prompt.\n\nWe need to good at Ansible, Terraform, Kubernetis things like that.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
